  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/81f04e60b9fcf8c9e55bcf3ca4a9e1c3.avif?t=1770017785\" width=1560 height=336 /></span>Bianca’s father is a myth buster who had to leave on a long journey, asking his daughter to clean the house, especially the attic. While doing so, Bianca discovers a strange old camera and starts taking pictures around the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What should have been an ordinary experience quickly turns upside down when she notices something unsettling: the photos reveal something her father always talked about, but she never truly believed, spirits from the underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rather than feeling scared, Bianca finds the discovery fascinating, until one of the photographed creatures takes offense at her curiosity. Determined to make Bianca delete the photos, it decides to get close to her by pretending to be her best friend for an entire week.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Bianca be convinced? Can true love blossom in just one week?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the answer in this cute and short yuri furry kinetic visual novel about girls and love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/9de116bf6f5c38b220c1bd232ac90457.avif?t=1770017785\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>A short and heartwarming yuri story;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span><strong>Kinetic visual novel</strong>, with an auto-read feature;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Furry CG artwork;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Steam achievements;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Duration: Around one hour.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/81f04e60b9fcf8c9e55bcf3ca4a9e1c3.avif?t=1770017785\" width=1560 height=336 /></span>Bianca’s father is a myth buster who had to leave on a long journey, asking his daughter to clean the house, especially the attic. While doing so, Bianca discovers a strange old camera and starts taking pictures around the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What should have been an ordinary experience quickly turns upside down when she notices something unsettling: the photos reveal something her father always talked about, but she never truly believed, spirits from the underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rather than feeling scared, Bianca finds the discovery fascinating, until one of the photographed creatures takes offense at her curiosity. Determined to make Bianca delete the photos, it decides to get close to her by pretending to be her best friend for an entire week.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Bianca be convinced? Can true love blossom in just one week?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the answer in this cute and short yuri furry kinetic visual novel about girls and love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/9de116bf6f5c38b220c1bd232ac90457.avif?t=1770017785\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>A short and heartwarming yuri story;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span><strong>Kinetic visual novel</strong>, with an auto-read feature;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Furry CG artwork;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Steam achievements;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Duration: Around one hour.</p>",
